---
layout: base.njk
title: ホーム
description: おうちヨガ・ウェルネスで毎日を整える。40〜50代女性のためのリアルな体験ブログ。
---

<style>
  .page-heading {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--green);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  /* カード型記事一覧 */
  .post-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }

  .post-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .post-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .post-card-thumb {
    background: var(--green-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 3rem;
    min-height: 140px;
  }

  .post-card-body {
    padding: 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .post-card-meta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .post-card-cat {
    background: var(--green-light);
    color: var(--green);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .post-card-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .post-card-title:hover { color: var(--green); }

  .post-card-excerpt {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .post-card-link {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .post-card-link::after { content: " →"; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .post-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .post-card-thumb { min-height: 120px; }
  }
</style>

<h2 class="page-heading">📝 新着記事</h2>

<div class="post-cards">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
  <article class="post-card">
    <div class="post-card-thumb">🧘</div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <div>
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <span>{{ post.date | dateJP }}</span>
          <span class="post-card-cat">ヨガ体験談</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="post-card-title">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        </h3>
        {% if post.data.description %}
        <p class="post-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card-link">続きを読む</a>
    </div>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
